  "parts": [
    {
      "name": "Section 1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "start": 98.28,
          "end": 99.4,
          "text": "MAN:Good morning.",
          "translation": "男：早上好。",
          "source_order": 0,
          "source_start_time": 98280,
          "source_end_time": 99400
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "start": 99.41,
          "end": 100.34,
          "text": "WOMAN:Good morning.",
          "translation": "女：早上好。",
          "source_order": 1,
          "source_start_time": 99410,
          "source_end_time": 100340
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "start": 100.35,
          "end": 101.54,
          "text": "How can I help you?",
          "translation": "有什么可以帮到您？",
          "source_order": 2,
          "source_start_time": 100350,
          "source_end_time": 101540
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "start": 101.55,
          "end": 104.46,
          "text": "MAN:I understand that the school organises...",
          "translation": "男：我了解到学校有组织",
          "source_order": 3,
          "source_start_time": 101550,
          "source_end_time": 104460
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "start": 105.1,
          "end": 106.4,
          "text": "umm, trips to different...",
          "translation": "去不同的地方旅行...",
          "source_order": 4,
          "source_start_time": 105100,
          "source_end_time": 106400
        },
        {
          "id": 6,
          "start": 145.96,
          "end": 152.15,
          "text": "WOMAN:Yes, we run five every month: three during weekends and two Wednesday afternoon trips.",
          "translation": "女：是的，我们每月共有五次，3次周末出发，2次周三下午出发。",
          "source_order": 5,
          "source_start_time": 145960,
          "source_end_time": 152150
        },
        {
          "id": 7,
          "start": 152.16,
          "end": 153.79,
          "text": "MAN:What sort of places?",
          "translation": "男：都去些什么地方呢？",
          "source_order": 6,
          "source_start_time": 152160,
          "source_end_time": 153790
        },
        {
          "id": 8,
          "start": 153.8,
          "end": 163.88,
          "text": "WOMAN:Well , obviously it varies , but always places of historical interest and also which offer a variety of shopping , because our students always ask about that...",
          "translation": "女：嗯，很多地方，但是都基本上是历史古迹。还有一系列购物点，因为学生总是咨询这些信息。",
          "source_order": 7,
          "source_start_time": 153800,
          "source_end_time": 163880
        },
        {
          "id": 9,
          "start": 164.42,
          "end": 170.01,
          "text": "and then we go for ones where we know there are guided tours , because this gives a good focus for the visit.",
          "translation": "我们会去有导游解说的地点，因为这样更有针对性。",
          "source_order": 8,
          "source_start_time": 164420,
          "source_end_time": 170010
        },
        {
          "id": 10,
          "start": 170.52,
          "end": 172.13,
          "text": "MAN:Do you travel far?",
          "translation": "男：去的地方远吗？",
          "source_order": 9,
          "source_start_time": 170520,
          "source_end_time": 172130
        },
        {
          "id": 11,
          "start": 172.17,
          "end": 179.08,
          "text": "WOMAN:Well, we're lucky here, obviously, because we're able to say that all our visits are less than three hours drive.",
          "translation": "女：嗯，我们显然是比较幸运的，可以这么说吧，我们的旅行团车程少于3小时。",
          "source_order": 10,
          "source_start_time": 172170,
          "source_end_time": 179080
        },
        {
          "id": 12,
          "start": 179.1,
          "end": 180.75,
          "text": "MAN:How much do they cost?",
          "translation": "男：价格多少呢？",
          "source_order": 11,
          "source_start_time": 179100,
          "source_end_time": 180750
        },
        {
          "id": 13,
          "start": 181.09,
          "end": 186.38,
          "text": "WOMAN:Again it varies - between five and fifteen pounds a head, depending on distance.",
          "translation": "女：这要看具体旅游团，根据距离的差异，每人五到十五镑之间。",
          "source_order": 12,
          "source_start_time": 181090,
          "source_end_time": 186380
        },
        {
          "id": 14,
          "start": 186.74,
          "end": 187.27,
          "text": "MAN:Ah ha ...",
          "translation": "男：啊...这样。",
          "source_order": 13,
          "source_start_time": 186740,
          "source_end_time": 187270
        },
        {
          "id": 15,
          "start": 187.06,
          "end": 193.26,
          "text": "WOMAN:Oh, and we do offer to arrange special trips if, you know, there are more than twelve people.",
          "translation": "女人：哦，还有如果你们超过12人，我们可以提供定制旅行团。",
          "source_order": 14,
          "source_start_time": 187060,
          "source_end_time": 193260
        },
        {
          "id": 16,
          "start": 193.6,
          "end": 194.02,
          "text": "MAN:Oh right.",
          "translation": "男：那好。",
          "source_order": 15,
          "source_start_time": 193600,
          "source_end_time": 194020
        },
        {
          "id": 17,
          "start": 194.02,
          "end": 195.36,
          "text": "I'll keep that in mind.",
          "translation": "我记住了。",
          "source_order": 16,
          "source_start_time": 194020,
          "source_end_time": 195360
        },
        {
          "id": 18,
          "start": 195.45,
          "end": 197.95,
          "text": "And what are the times normally?",
          "translation": "通常什么时间出发呢？",
          "source_order": 17,
          "source_start_time": 195450,
          "source_end_time": 197950
        },
        {
          "id": 19,
          "start": 197.96,
          "end": 203.3,
          "text": "WOMAN:We try to keep it pretty fixed so that, that students get to know the pattern.",
          "translation": "女：我们尽量固定时间，好让学生知道我们的出团模式。",
          "source_order": 18,
          "source_start_time": 197960,
          "source_end_time": 203300
        },
        {
          "id": 20,
          "start": 203.48,
          "end": 207.66,
          "text": "We leave at eight-thirty a. m. and return at six p. m.p.",
          "translation": "我们早上八点半出发，下午六点回程。",
          "source_order": 19,
          "source_start_time": 203480,
          "source_end_time": 207660
        },
        {
          "id": 21,
          "start": 207.67,
          "end": 210.27,
          "text": "We figure it's best to keep the day fairly short.",
          "translation": "我们觉得最好还是短途的。",
          "source_order": 20,
          "source_start_time": 207670,
          "source_end_time": 210270
        },
        {
          "id": 22,
          "start": 210.34,
          "end": 211.16,
          "text": "MAN:Oh yes.",
          "translation": "男：哦，对，",
          "source_order": 21,
          "source_start_time": 210340,
          "source_end_time": 211160
        },
        {
          "id": 23,
          "start": 211.32,
          "end": 214.26,
          "text": "And how do we reserve a place?",
          "translation": "那我们怎么预订呢？",
          "source_order": 22,
          "source_start_time": 211320,
          "source_end_time": 214260
        },
        {
          "id": 24,
          "start": 214.27,
          "end": 216.31,
          "text": "WOMAN:You sign your name on the notice board.",
          "translation": "女：在公告栏上签名就好。",
          "source_order": 23,
          "source_start_time": 214270,
          "source_end_time": 216310
        },
        {
          "id": 25,
          "start": 216.35,
          "end": 217.51,
          "text": "Do you know where it is?",
          "translation": "你知道在哪里吗？",
          "source_order": 24,
          "source_start_time": 216350,
          "source_end_time": 217510
        },
        {
          "id": 26,
          "start": 217.72,
          "end": 217.87,
          "text": "MAN:Ah ha.",
          "translation": "男：嗯，",
          "source_order": 25,
          "source_start_time": 217720,
          "source_end_time": 217869
        },
        {
          "id": 27,
          "start": 217.95,
          "end": 219.48,
          "text": "I saw it this morning.",
          "translation": "今天早上我看见了。",
          "source_order": 26,
          "source_start_time": 217950,
          "source_end_time": 219480
        },
        {
          "id": 28,
          "start": 219.49,
          "end": 229.93,
          "text": "WOMAN:And we do ask that you sign up three days in advance so we know we've got enough people interested to run it, and we can cancel if necessary, with full refund of course.",
          "translation": "女：我们要求提前三天签名，这样我们就能统计感兴趣的人数了。如果有必要我们会取消发团，当然报名费会全额退款。",
          "source_order": 27,
          "source_start_time": 219490,
          "source_end_time": 229930
        },
        {
          "id": 29,
          "start": 229.94,
          "end": 231.62,
          "text": "MAN:That's fine, thanks.",
          "translation": "男：那好，谢谢。",
          "source_order": 28,
          "source_start_time": 229940,
          "source_end_time": 231620
        },
        {
          "id": 30,
          "start": 266.8,
          "end": 269.61,
          "text": "And what visits are planned for this term?",
          "translation": "这个学期有什么出团安排呢？",
          "source_order": 29,
          "source_start_time": 266800,
          "source_end_time": 269610
        },
        {
          "id": 31,
          "start": 269.7,
          "end": 282.42,
          "text": "WOMAN:Right, well I'm afraid the schedule hasn't been printed out yet, but we have confirmed the dates and planned the optional extra visits which you can also book in advance if you want to.",
          "translation": "女：对，我估计这个学期的计划表还没打印出来。但是我们已经确认好出团日期以及计划好额外的旅行团，如果你想提前预定也可以。",
          "source_order": 30,
          "source_start_time": 269700,
          "source_end_time": 282420
        },
        {
          "id": 32,
          "start": 283.1,
          "end": 283.98,
          "text": "MAN:Oh that's all right.",
          "translation": "男：哦，那可以。",
          "source_order": 31,
          "source_start_time": 283100,
          "source_end_time": 283980
        },
        {
          "id": 33,
          "start": 284.56,
          "end": 291.4,
          "text": "If you can just give some idea of the weekend ones so I can, you know, work out when to see friends, etcetera.",
          "translation": "如果你能先给我周末的出团信息，这样我就好安排什么时候见朋友等等。",
          "source_order": 32,
          "source_start_time": 284560,
          "source_end_time": 291400
        },
        {
          "id": 34,
          "start": 291.44,
          "end": 292.02,
          "text": "WOMAN:Oh sure.",
          "translation": "女：哦，没问题。",
          "source_order": 33,
          "source_start_time": 291440,
          "source_end_time": 292020
        },
        {
          "id": 35,
          "start": 292.83,
          "end": 297.23,
          "text": "Well, the first one is St Ives.",
          "translation": "第一个是圣艾夫斯。",
          "source_order": 34,
          "source_start_time": 292830,
          "source_end_time": 297230
        },
        {
          "id": 36,
          "start": 297.25,
          "end": 304.6,
          "text": "That's on the thirteenth of February and we'll have only sixteen places available because we're going by minibus.",
          "translation": "是在二月十三日去，我们只有16空位，因为我们是坐小巴去。",
          "source_order": 35,
          "source_start_time": 297250,
          "source_end_time": 304600
        },
        {
          "id": 37,
          "start": 305.04,
          "end": 310.35,
          "text": "And that's a day in town with the optional extra of visiting the Hepworth Museum.",
          "translation": "这个团是小镇一日游，可额外选择参观海浦沃斯博物馆。",
          "source_order": 36,
          "source_start_time": 305040,
          "source_end_time": 310350
        },
        {
          "id": 38,
          "start": 310.37,
          "end": 311.08,
          "text": "MAN:Oh right...",
          "translation": "男：哦，好的…",
          "source_order": 37,
          "source_start_time": 310370,
          "source_end_time": 311080
        },
        {
          "id": 39,
          "start": 311.08,
          "end": 311.42,
          "text": "yeah...",
          "translation": "好…",
          "source_order": 38,
          "source_start_time": 311080,
          "source_end_time": 311420
        },
        {
          "id": 40,
          "start": 311.42,
          "end": 312.61,
          "text": "that sounds good.",
          "translation": "听起来不错。",
          "source_order": 39,
          "source_start_time": 311420,
          "source_end_time": 312610
        },
        {
          "id": 41,
          "start": 313.69,
          "end": 327.95,
          "text": "WOMAN:Then there's a London trip on the sixteenth of February and we'll be taking a medium-sized coach so there'll be forty-five places on that, and, let's see, the optional extra is the Tower of London.",
          "translation": "女：然后2月16号还有一个伦敦游团，我们坐中型客车，所以那上面有45个位置。让我看看，这个团可额外选择参观伦敦塔。",
          "source_order": 40,
          "source_start_time": 313690,
          "source_end_time": 327950
        },
        {
          "id": 42,
          "start": 327.96,
          "end": 330.01,
          "text": "MAN:Oh, I've already been there.",
          "translation": "男：哦，我已经去过那里了。",
          "source_order": 41,
          "source_start_time": 327960,
          "source_end_time": 330010
        },
        {
          "id": 43,
          "start": 331.08,
          "end": 333.98,
          "text": "WOMAN:After that there's Brisiol on the third of March.",
          "translation": "女：呃，这个团之后是3月3号布里斯托团。",
          "source_order": 42,
          "source_start_time": 331080,
          "source_end_time": 333980
        },
        {
          "id": 44,
          "start": 351.56,
          "end": 351.94,
          "text": "MAN:Where?",
          "translation": "男：哪儿？",
          "source_order": 43,
          "source_start_time": 351560,
          "source_end_time": 351940
        },
        {
          "id": 45,
          "start": 335.07,
          "end": 335.66,
          "text": "WOMAN:Bristol...",
          "translation": "女：布里斯托…",
          "source_order": 44,
          "source_start_time": 335070,
          "source_end_time": 335659
        },
        {
          "id": 46,
          "start": 335.97,
          "end": 338.2,
          "text": "B-R-I-S-T-O-L.",
          "translation": "B-R-I-S-T-O-L.",
          "source_order": 45,
          "source_start_time": 335969,
          "source_end_time": 338199
        },
        {
          "id": 47,
          "start": 338.25,
          "end": 338.88,
          "text": "MAN:OK..",
          "translation": "男：好的…",
          "source_order": 46,
          "source_start_time": 338250,
          "source_end_time": 338880
        },
        {
          "id": 48,
          "start": 339.48,
          "end": 349.92,
          "text": "WOMAN:That's in a different minibus with eighteen places available , oh , and the optional extra is a visit to the S. S. Great Britain.",
          "translation": "女：那是乘坐有18个座位的另一种小巴。可额外选择参观大不列颠号。",
          "source_order": 47,
          "source_start_time": 339480,
          "source_end_time": 349920
        },
        {
          "id": 49,
          "start": 349.96,
          "end": 350.64,
          "text": "MAN:OK...",
          "translation": "男：好吧。",
          "source_order": 48,
          "source_start_time": 349960,
          "source_end_time": 350640
        },
        {
          "id": 50,
          "start": 351.94,
          "end": 363.1,
          "text": "WOMAN:We're going to Salisbury on the eighteenth of March and that's always a popular one because the optional extra is Stonehenge, so we're taking the large coach with fifty seats...",
          "translation": "女：3月18号是索尔兹伯里的团，这个团很受欢迎，因为可以额外选择参观巨石阵。所以我们会乘坐50人的大巴车。",
          "source_order": 49,
          "source_start_time": 351940,
          "source_end_time": 363100
        },
        {
          "id": 51,
          "start": 363.24,
          "end": 364.0,
          "text": "MAN:Oh good.",
          "translation": "男：哦，很好啊。",
          "source_order": 50,
          "source_start_time": 363240,
          "source_end_time": 364000
        },
        {
          "id": 52,
          "start": 364.58,
          "end": 368.96,
          "text": "WOMAN:And then the last one is to Bath on the twenty-third of March.",
          "translation": "女：最后一个是3月23号去巴斯。",
          "source_order": 51,
          "source_start_time": 364580,
          "source_end_time": 368960
        },
        {
          "id": 53,
          "start": 368.97,
          "end": 369.72,
          "text": "MAN:Oh yes.",
          "translation": "男人：是吗，",
          "source_order": 52,
          "source_start_time": 368970,
          "source_end_time": 369720
        },
        {
          "id": 54,
          "start": 369.73,
          "end": 371.97,
          "text": "Is Bath the Roman city?",
          "translation": "巴斯是那个罗马城市吗？",
          "source_order": 53,
          "source_start_time": 369730,
          "source_end_time": 371970
        },
        {
          "id": 55,
          "start": 371.99,
          "end": 372.26,
          "text": "WOMAN:Yes.",
          "translation": "女：对啊。",
          "source_order": 54,
          "source_start_time": 371990,
          "source_end_time": 372260
        },
        {
          "id": 56,
          "start": 372.26,
          "end": 375.82,
          "text": "that's right, and that's in the sixteen-seater minibus.",
          "translation": "这个会坐16座的小巴。",
          "source_order": 55,
          "source_start_time": 372260,
          "source_end_time": 375820
        },
        {
          "id": 57,
          "start": 375.83,
          "end": 377.96,
          "text": "MAN:And where's the optional visit?",
          "translation": "男：额外景点是？",
          "source_order": 56,
          "source_start_time": 375830,
          "source_end_time": 377960
        },
        {
          "id": 58,
          "start": 377.97,
          "end": 381.14,
          "text": "WOMAN:It's to the American Museum - well worth a visit.",
          "translation": "女：是去美国博物馆，那是个很值得去的景点。",
          "source_order": 57,
          "source_start_time": 377970,
          "source_end_time": 381140
        },
        {
          "id": 59,
          "start": 381.18,
          "end": 381.87,
          "text": "MAN:OK.",
          "translation": "男：好的。",
          "source_order": 58,
          "source_start_time": 381180,
          "source_end_time": 381870
        },
        {
          "id": 60,
          "start": 381.92,
          "end": 384.6,
          "text": "well that's great, thanks for all that...",
          "translation": "真好，谢谢你啊。",
          "source_order": 59,
          "source_start_time": 381920,
          "source_end_time": 384600
        },
        {
          "id": 61,
          "start": 384.8,
          "end": 385.74,
          "text": "WOMAN:My pleasure.",
          "translation": "女：不客气。",
          "source_order": 60,
          "source_start_time": 384800,
          "source_end_time": 385740
        },
        {
          "id": 62,
          "start": 386.17,
          "end": 391.77,
          "text": "By the way, if you want more information about any of the trips, have a look in the student newspaper.",
          "translation": "顺便说下，如果想了解更多旅行团信息，你可以浏览学生报。",
          "source_order": 61,
          "source_start_time": 386170,
          "source_end_time": 391770
        },
        {
          "id": 63,
          "start": 391.82,
          "end": 392.41,
          "text": "MAN:OK.",
          "translation": "男：好的。",
          "source_order": 62,
          "source_start_time": 391820,
          "source_end_time": 392409
        },
        {
          "id": 64,
          "start": 392.64,
          "end": 395.07,
          "text": "WOMAN:Or, have a word with my assistant;",
          "translation": "女：或者可以问下我助手，",
          "source_order": 63,
          "source_start_time": 392640,
          "source_end_time": 395070
        },
        {
          "id": 65,
          "start": 395.14,
          "end": 398.7,
          "text": "her name is Jane Yentob - that's Y-E-N-T-O-B.",
          "translation": "她叫简·严拓，就是YENTOB。",
          "source_order": 64,
          "source_start_time": 395140,
          "source_end_time": 398700
        },
        {
          "id": 66,
          "start": 400.64,
          "end": 402.32,
          "text": "MAN:Right, I've got that.",
          "translation": "男：好，我知道了。",
          "source_order": 65,
          "source_start_time": 400640,
          "source_end_time": 402320
        },
        {
          "id": 67,
          "start": 402.39,
          "end": 404.19,
          "text": "Thank you very much for all your help.",
